%%Example 1
st||pn|You,Opener,Partner (overcaller),|RH||ah|Example 1|md|2SK Q 98 H 87 D A 654 C854,,,|sv|o|MB|1h1np?|lb|*bWhat bid would you make?^^2c|NT|^B@2
You bid 2@C to ask if partner has a 4-card spade suit. Notrumper knows you are asking for a 4+-card spade suit and not heart suit (opener bid 1@H). Just as over a 1NT opening, you generally needs at least an invitational strength hand to use the Stayman convention.|mb|2c|
