Some partnership do not play "Systems On-Stolen Bid." Because if they do the 2@S by notrumper is not forcing and the South hand is strong enough which can play either in 3N or 4@S. Therefore, you bid 3@S|MB|3S|AT| and giving overcaller the choice of setting the contract in either 3N or 4@S.|
