Other partnerships think "Systems On-Stolen Bid" certainly works on this hand. You double as a spade transfer and then bid 3@H which denies a spade stopper. Pard will usually then bid 4@S or 3N. With only 2 card spade support and no heart stopper pard will either bid 3@S or a 5-card minor.
|
