Just like responding to 2N opener,  3@C would be Stayman, 3@D would be a transfer to hearts, and 3@S probably would mean transfer to minors. Again with LHO bidding 2@S, South hardly ever would have a hand needing transfer to spades. So 3@H bid by South would never be a needed. |
