NT|^B@2
With this hand, you bid 3@C as the Stayman convention, to see if partner has at four-card heart suit. You have 12 HCP, which would be enough to consider a slam if North had opened 2NT, showing 20-21 points. North's 2NT overcall as you know, however, only shows about 15-18 points. So forget the slam.|
