NT|^B@2
Many partnerships use the same pattern as with 1NT and 2NT overcalls. Therefore, 4@C would be Stayman, and 4@D and 4@H would be transfer bids. Further, it is possible, assuming you have enough room, to play "Systems On-Stolen Bid."|
